target.mrk: <MadCap:variable name="ModuleAndDevicesNames.MCScap-NTH_name" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> is a high cup Ag / AgCl sintered electrode for EEG recording.
The shape of the electrode in the form like a high bowl, which provides tighter contact with the patient's skin in thick hair.
